# CLAD local configuration for Roo Code modes
# Copy this file to .roo-clad-config and fill in values for your project.
# .roo-clad-config is gitignored — it is yours alone.

## Test command
# The command Roo will run after each implementation edit in clad-green mode.
# Examples:
#   ./mvnw test -pl reference-impl/java-micronaut-jena
#   ./gradlew test
#   npm test
TEST_COMMAND=./mvnw test

## Profile storage layer
# The storage technology used by this project's reference-impl profile.
# Roo will use this description when enforcing the no-in-memory-substitute rule.
# Examples:
#   Jena TDB2 named graph (Java/Micronaut profile)
#   PostgreSQL schema per concept (Spring Boot profile)
#   MongoDB collection per concept (Node.js profile)
STORAGE_LAYER=Jena TDB2 named graph (Java/Micronaut profile)
